			<h2 class="excerpt-title"><a href="https://mondaymandala.com/coloring-pages-for-toddlers/" class="excerpt-link">Coloring Pages for Toddlers (Free PDF Printables)</a></h2>
			<div class="excerpt-excerpt">
				<p>Big shapes, friendly faces, and easy lines fill these 50 coloring pages for toddlers, free to download and print! Designed with little hands and developing skills in mind, these pages offer simple, high-contrast designs perfect for early learners just starting to explore crayons and colour. You&rsquo;ll find toddler-friendly illustrations of smiling animals, chunky vehicles, fruits &hellip;</p>
